highlights.text: “No Broke Boys” by Disco Lines and Tinashe has been on Viral Songs Norway the longest, at 93 days straight.
“Confess Your Love” by Jiandro and ola.wav is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Norway, up 21 spots at #62.
Breizaas has the most spots on Viral Songs Norway. “Balanserer på en tynn en” is the highest at #39.
“True Believer” by Biffy Clyro is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Norway at #97.
